<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Dumbbell-Lateral-Raise">Dumbbell Lateral Raise</h3>



<p>One of the best upper body exercises to implement is <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-lateral-raise" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">lateral raises</a>. It works on all of your shoulder muscle groups, primarily targeting the shoulder muscles, specifically the lateral deltoids.</p>



<p>The exercise enhances shoulder definition and widens the upper body appearance, creating a balanced physique. It also strengthens the shoulder muscles, improving overall shoulder stability and reducing the risk of injury.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio vimeo-custom"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
