<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Cable-Tricep-Pushdown">Cable Tricep Pushdown</h3>



<p>The <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/cable-tricep-pushdown" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">cable tricep pushdown</a> is a popular exercise that isolates the three tricep muscle heads. It’s easy to perform and can be done using a wide range of cable attachments. Alongside this, it’s a good way to improve upper-arm aesthetics.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The primary movers are the tricep brachii muscle heads. They work to extend the elbows as you push the attachment towards the floor.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio vimeo-custom"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
