                                </div>
                                <p class="has-medium-font-size">Sternal Head of Pectoralis Major</p>
                                <p class="has-small-font-size muslce-ds">Large muscles located underneath your clavicle head. Makes up most of your chest area </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                                                                                <div class="mucle">
                            <div class="muscle-item">
