                                </div>
                                <p class="has-medium-font-size">Lateral Deltoid</p>
                                <p class="has-small-font-size muslce-ds"><p>Muscles located at the side of your shoulder which gives your shoulders a rounded appearance.</p></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
